text.section:
If a certificate of declination is filed under this section:
the certificate of nomination to which the certificate of declination relates is void;
a vacancy in nomination is created to be filled in accordance with the provisions of Subtitle 10 of this title;
the name of the individual who declined the nomination may not appear on the ballot unless the individual is selected to fill that vacancy; and
the filing fee for the certificate of candidacy of that individual may not be refunded.
